<br>
At 25 and solo, I would suggest you stick strictly to the magicians. Avoid the TT by staying in the middle of the large room when going through it. Summon an earth pet and have it at all times. If things go terribly wrong, it will buy you enough time to zone or gate.   The skeletons there are around lvl 21-24.  You can take them, just watch for adds.  <br>
<br>
There are 4 magicians that you can safely solo at 25. There are two together in the Crystal room, and 2 singles on the path to the crystal room. These can all be taken effectively at 25. Sic your pet on the other pet first, then burn the magician down as fast as possible.<br>
<br>
Stay away from the magicians in Rathyl's room and Trazdon's room. You can take them, but at 25, Trazdon, Rathyl, and Rathyl's incarnate will hand you your butt in tiny, manageable chunks. It is still a close shave at 42 to break the Rathyl room.<br>
<br>
Best advice, get some resist gear. You are going against mage and necro casters, so get your magic, fire, and poison resists pretty high. A couple of Star Ruby Encrusted Steins will help greatly.<br>
<br>
And keep checking the bazaar. I've rarely seen the focus ingredients very high. You might get lucky and get them for about 10pp. <p><DIV style="position:relative; width=80%; filter:Blur(Add = 1, Direction = 225, Strength = 10)">
